  "text": "EBITDA reached $36.6B in Q2 2025, translating to a 21.82% EBITDA margin that underscores strong operational cash generation. Operating cash flow of $32.5B supported capital deployment, though free cash flow remained modest at $332M (0.20% FCF margin) due to elevated capital expenditures of $32.2B. This represents a meaningful improvement from Q1's negative $8.0B free cash flow, suggesting better cash conversion as the quarter progressed.",
